{"title":"七月","authors":["木斧"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":7,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七　月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木　斧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月到了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄澄澄的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉甸甸的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂满了晶莹的露珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈着琐碎的步子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地拍着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每家每户的门窗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郁热将要过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用不着唠唠叨叨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱怨那发霉的日子啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦一擦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抹掉那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伤心的往事……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树林染绿了阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们摇着蒲扇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在树荫下乘凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝一口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爽心的浓茶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桂花飘香！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳收敛了它的锋芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变得暖洋洋的了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它仍以犀利的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梭巡着大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许寒冷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偷偷袭来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用担心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它会烤灼肌肤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看它的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比任何时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更柔和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更裸露……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱走疲劳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶跑困倦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要收获去了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将收获"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜悦的汗珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我惊奇地发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕是一滴汗珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没有白白抛洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它象珍珠一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪闪发光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将继续播种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用什么献给土地呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么果实最多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么品种更新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么滋味最鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我沉醉了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将播种什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我象蜜蜂一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细心地酝酿啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}